We welcome you to any and all of NOBO's special events!
Please check out our Events Page on
Facebook
, Untappd or our
website
for complete rundown of what's happening in and around the brewery. Please like our Facebook page, if you haven't already, to get the latest updates around special events, food trucks and beer releases. We wouldn't want you to miss a thing!
Interested in having your event or party at NOBO?
We'd love to have you! We have a new private event space that would be perfect for your next event! Just give us a
call
, come on in
or contact us via
email
or
Facebook
. We will get back to you as soon as possible to get your questions answered and your event scheduled.
We hope to see you & your group very soon!
